<li><a href=\"http://www.bariol.com/\">Cheap but beautiful rounded font</a><br/>
Very nice.</li>
<li><a href=\"http://martinmelin.se/rewrite-rule-tester/\">Test your RewriteRules for Apache mod_rewrite</a><br/>
